Amazon Web Services (AWS) is the world's most comprehensive and broadly adopted cloud platform, offering over 200 fully featured services from global data centers. It provides on-demand, pay-as-you-go access to compute, storage, databases, and advanced technologies like AI/ML, enabling scalable, secure, and cost-effective IT infrastructure without upfront expenses. 
